  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose  of the present study is  to determine the influence of position of soft tissue
      repair (flexion versus extension) in post operative range of motion(ROM) and functional
      outcome in patients who underwent primary total knee arthroplasty (TKA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
